Package bzh.plealog.hge.api.datamodel Description

The "datamodel" package provides the interfaces to describe real world data as an hyper-graph.

Actually, the idea of an hyper-graph is here very shallow. It mostly means that you'll have to describe your data using a DataGraphModel that is made of DGMVertexType and DGMHyperEdgeType, each of them containing some DGMAttribute.

DGMVertexType and DGMHyperEdgeType can be organized using hierarchies (types and sub-types). This hierarchical data model only support single inheritance.
